	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />That's a good argument for an option to leave the endless mode the way it is when I add a round limit.<br /><br />Anyway, I was able to reproduce one of the bugs (failure to remove some garden plants that have become surrounded by walls), and I fixed it in my tree. The other (corruption of the Stock screen's state producing a pile of 255s) I have no idea about, as I only saw it happen once on hardware and wasn't running any sort of video recording, but I've added some bounds checks to make it less visible in case it is what I think it might be.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


